icious blessing and health (connected to earlier rik RV10.015=\r\n.03 - where the invokation was for progeny =C2=A0- napaataM =C2=A0to contin=\r\nue with yaGYa - viShNoH)\n\n=C2=A0 references: Vedic reader by A.A. MacDonell=\r\n, Monier Williams and Mac Donell dictionaries via Mudgala Kosha, Roots and =\r\nVerb-Forms by W.D. Whitney, Vedic Grammar by AA MacDonell, all these refere=\r\nnces are freely available on the internet.\n\nRegards,\nsarma.\n=C2=A0=C2=A0\n \r\n---435270448-1671952794-1316249062=:8547\r\nContent-Type: text/html; charset=utf-8\r\nContent-Transfer-Encoding: quoted-printable\r\n\r\n&lt;html&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;color:#000; background-color:#fff; font-family:ti=\r\nmes new roman, new york, times, serif;font-size:12pt&quot;&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;Dear all, =\r\nThere is also a Yajur Veda Mantra &quot;Pitrun Prinani&quot; which is generally chant=\r\ned after ashirwadham mantras, I was told its on the Samhita 5th Kanda.. Can=\r\n some one help me locate the text/audio .&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br&gt;=\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;Thanks &amp; Rgds&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;sa&lt;/span&gt;&lt;=\r\n/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: &#39;times new =\r\nroman&#39;, &#39;new york&#39;, times, serif; &quot;&gt;&lt;div style=3D&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-fam=\r\nily: &#39;times new roman&#39;, &#39;new york&#39;, times, serif; &quot;&gt;&lt;font size=3D&quot;2&quot; face=\r\n=3D&quot;Arial&quot;&gt;&lt;hr size=3D&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;font-weight:bold;&quot;&gt;From:&lt;/span&gt;=\r\n&lt;/b&gt; agnijihva &lt;agnijihva@...&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;font-weight=\r\n: bold;&quot;&gt;To:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; vedic-wisdom@yahoogroups.com&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;f=\r\nont-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Sent:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; Saturday, September 17, 20